{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to Miami, the city of sun, sand, and neon lights! In <strong>Miami Hotel Simulator</strong>, you and your friends team up to renovate, manage, and grow your very own hotel. Work together in <strong>multiplayer</strong> mode to clean rooms, serve guests, and keep your customers happy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You've just bought an old hotel in the heart of Miami. Your job? Turn it into a luxurious retreat that brings in big profits. Upgrade the hotel, manage guest services, and watch as visitors spend on your slot machines, restaurants, and bars, fueling your success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But it's not all sunshine\u2014more guests mean more mess. You\u2019ll have to deal with garbage, clogged toilets, and messy rooms before new guests can check in. The more you manage, the more you can profit and customize your hotel, creating a space that reflects your style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer</strong>: Manage the hotel with your friends, delegate tasks, and work as a team.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hotel Customization</strong>: Design and upgrade every part of your hotel to attract more guests and maximize profits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Challenges</strong>: Handle guest messes, maintain your hotel, and keep customers coming back for more.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Jump into <strong>Miami Hotel Simulator</strong> and turn your hotel into a paradise in the city of neon!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1936810?t=1740140338","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1936810?t=1740140338","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.stea